{{神社
|名称={{ill|Kotozaki Hachiman Shrine|ja|琴崎八幡宮}}
|画像 = [[File:Kotozakihachiman.JPG|260px]]
|所在地={{ill|Yamaguchi Prefecture|ja|山口県}}{{ill|Ube|ja|宇部市}}上宇部大小路
|位置={{ウィキ座標2段度分秒|33|58|18|N|131|16|13|E|region:JP-35_type:landmark|display=inline,title}}
|祭神={{ill|Hondawake no Mikoto|ja|品陀和気命}}<br/>{{ill|Okinaga Tarashihime|ja|気長足比女命}}<br/>{{ill|Chūai|ja|足仲津比古命}}
|社格={{ill|Prefectural shrine|ja|県社}}・{{ill|Beppyo shrine|ja|別表神社}}
|創建={{ill|Jōgan (Japan)|ja|貞観}}元年（{{ill|859|ja|859年}}）
|例祭={{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日}}
}}
'''Kotozaki Hachiman Shrine'''（琴崎八幡宮[[ja:琴崎八幡宮]]）は、{{ill|Yamaguchi Prefecture|ja|山口県}}{{ill|Ube|ja|宇部市}}にある{{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社}}。旧{{ill|Modern shrine ranking system|ja|近代社格制度}}の社格は{{ill|Prefectural shrine|ja|県社}}で、現在は{{ill|Association of Shinto Shrines|ja|神社本庁}}の{{ill|Beppyo shrine|ja|別表神社}}。宇部市の総鎮守として崇敬を受ける。

{{ill|Hachiman|ja|八幡神}}（{{ill|Hondawake no Mikoto|ja|品陀和気命}}・{{ill|Okinaga Tarashihime|ja|気長足比女命}}・{{ill|Chūai|ja|足仲津比古命}}）を主{{ill|Kami|ja|祭神}}とし、{{ill|Munakata Sanjojin|ja|宗像三女神}}（{{ill|Tagirihime|ja|多紀理比女命}}・{{ill|Tatsutsuhime|ja|多紀津比女命}}・{{ill|Ichikishimahime|ja|市杵島比女命}}）を配祀する。

== History ==
According to the shrine's tradition, in {{ill|Jōgan (Japan)|ja|貞観}}元年（{{ill|859|ja|859年}}）, {{ill|Gyōkyō|ja|行教}} established a temporary palace at Koteshima Bay in Ube during his journey from {{ill|Usa Shrine|ja|宇佐}} to {{ill|Iwashimizu Hachimangū|ja|石清水}} to enshrine Hachiman. Villagers enshrined the divided spirit of Hachiman on the site. In {{ill|Tenchū 3|ja|天授3年}}（{{ill|1377|ja|1377年}}）, following an oracle, the shrine was relocated to its current location at Kotozaki. It received the patronage of successive feudal lords, including the {{ill|Kuto clan|ja|厚東氏}}, the {{ill|Ōuchi clan|ja|大内氏}}, and the {{ill|Mōri clan|ja|毛利氏}}.

In {{ill|1873|ja|明治6年}}, the shrine was designated a {{ill|Gōsha|ja|郷社}}, and in {{ill|1938|ja|昭和13年}}, it was promoted to a {{ill|Prefectural shrine|ja|県社}}. In July {{ill|1966|ja|昭和41年}}, it was listed as a {{ill|Beppyo shrine|ja|別表神社}} by the {{ill|Association of Shinto Shrines|ja|神社本庁}}.

== Transportation Access ==
; By Car
* About 3 minutes from {{ill|Sanyo Expressway|ja|山陽自動車道}}{{ill|Ube Interchange|ja|宇部インターチェンジ}}.
* About 15 minutes from {{ill|Yamaguchi Ube Airport|ja|山口宇部空港}}.
* About 20 minutes from {{ill|Shin-Yamaguchi Station|ja|新山口駅}} by {{ill|JR|ja|西日本旅客鉄道}}.

